{
  "stem": "15082.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The reason that we left Dubno, we did not want to wind up in the Russians, again, because we knew that it wasn't a way of life.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a way to stay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were able to-- they were going to take us to further deep into Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So our hope was to get over somehow to the German side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we boarded a train, an open train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we traveled from Dubno through Czechoslovakia-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, no, from Dubno, we traveled into [NON-ENGLISH], which was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We arrived there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got off the train, again, about I'd say 30, 40 Jewish families that we travelled with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we settled in [NON-ENGLISH], which was near Katowice, was the big-- very big town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] was a nice sized town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Again, we found a place to live in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And little by little, the town-- again, [NON-ENGLISH] started to fill up with Jews that were running away from that part of the Ukraine, getting in deeper, closer to the Czechoslovakia border.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Actually, the next border would have been Czechoslovakia, and into Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What my dad did-- this-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] little by little, they started like handling, and doing a little business, and just to support themselves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just eking out and make a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was nothing substantial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't really set up home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just a way of, again, surviving, and trying to make the best of it, knowing that, eventually, you want to get to a place, a destination, whether it would be Israel of America.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the hope then that everybody had in mind, is to get out of Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
